---
import SiteLayout from "../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout title="Tax Help | ImmediateLawyerHelp.com">
  <section class="taxHero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="heroCard">
        <h1>Tax help from experienced attorneys</h1>
        <p class="sub">
          Get routed to an attorney for audits, tax debt, liens/levies, and complex IRS matters.
        </p>

        <form class="searchRow" action="/legalform/" method="get">
          <input
            name="q"
            type="text"
            placeholder="What tax issue do you need help with?"
            aria-label="Describe your tax issue"
          />
          <button type="submit">Get Started</button>
        </form>

        <div class="heroMeta">
          <span>Fast</span><span class="dot">•</span>
          <span>Confidential</span><span class="dot">•</span>
          <span>No cost to begin</span><span class="dot">•</span>
          <span>Independent attorneys</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="taxScope">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid">
        <article class="featureCard">
          <div class="media" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="body">
            <h2>Individual tax matters</h2>
            <p class="muted">Common reasons people reach out for help.</p>
            <ul class="checkList">
              <li>IRS Audits &amp; Examinations</li>
              <li>Back Taxes &amp; Tax Debt</li>
              <li>Tax Liens &amp; Levies</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="featureCard">
          <div class="media alt" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="body">
            <h2>Business tax matters</h2>
            <p class="muted">Guidance for companies and owners.</p>
            <ul class="checkList">
              <li>Unified Tax Returns</li>
              <li>Business &amp; Payroll Tax Issues</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>


     <div class="ctaStrip infoBlock centered withImage right">
        <div class="text">
          <h3>Why tax issues often get worse over time</h3>
          <p class="muted">
            Many tax problems don’t resolve on their own. Penalties, interest, and enforcement actions can continue even
            when you’re actively trying to fix the issue. Missing deadlines or responding incorrectly to IRS notices can
            unintentionally make things more complex.
          </p>
          <p class="muted">Getting guidance early can help clarify your options and prevent unnecessary escalation.</p>
        </div>
          <div class="image"><img src="/assets/tax-escalation.png" alt="" /></div>
      </div>

      <div class="ctaStrip infoBlock centered withImage left">
        <div class="text">
          <h3>How a tax attorney can help</h3>
          <ul class="bulletList">
            <li>Communicating with the IRS or state tax authorities</li>
            <li>Reviewing notices, audits, and prior filings</li>
            <li>Explaining resolution options (payment plans, settlements, and other paths)</li>
            <li>Advising on rights, obligations, and next steps</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="muted">The right approach depends on your specific situation and the type of issue involved.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="image"><img src="/assets/tax-attorney-help.png" alt="" /></div>
      </div>

      <div class="ctaStrip infoBlock centered">
        <div>
          <h3>Common situations people reach out about</h3>
          <ul class="bulletList">
            <li>Receiving an IRS audit or examination notice</li>
            <li>Owing back taxes from prior years</li>
            <li>Wage garnishments, liens, or levies</li>
            <li>Payroll or business tax disputes</li>
            <li>Unfiled or incorrect returns</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="muted">
            Even if your situation doesn’t fit neatly into a category, describe what’s happening and we’ll route you
            accordingly.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ctaStrip infoBlock centered">
        <div>
          <h3>What to expect when you get started</h3>
          <p class="muted">
            You’ll answer a few questions about your situation so we can identify the appropriate type of tax attorney.
            There’s no obligation to move forward, and no cost to begin.
          </p>
          <p class="muted">
            We focus on connecting people with attorneys experienced in tax matters, not selling tax services directly.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ctaStrip infoBlock centered">
        <div>
          <h3>Frequently asked questions</h3>

          <details class="qa">
  <summary class="q">Do I need a tax attorney or a CPA?</summary>
  <div class="a muted">
    Tax attorneys focus on legal rights, disputes, and representation in tax matters. A CPA may handle
              preparation and accounting, but may not represent you in all disputes.
  </div>
</details>

          <details class="qa">
  <summary class="q">Can someone help if I already owe money?</summary>
  <div class="a muted">
    Yes. Owing back taxes is one of the most common reasons people seek legal guidance.
  </div>
</details>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ctaStrip">
        <div>
          <h3>Not sure what category fits?</h3>
          <p class="muted">Describe what’s happening and we’ll route you to the right attorney type.</p>
        </div>
        <a class="ctaBtn" href="/legalform/">Start</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .taxHero{
      position: relative;
      padding: 72px 0 56px;
      background: radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 50% 0%, rgba(12, 42, 92, .18), transparent 60%),
                  linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,.03), rgba(0,0,0,0));
    }
    .container{ max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
    .heroCard{
      max-width: 820px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    }
    h1{ font-size: 44px; line-height: 1.1; margin: 0 0 10px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .sub{ margin: 0 0 18px; color: rgba(0,0,0,.68); font-size: 16px; }
    .searchRow{
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: center;
      margin: 10px 0 12px;
    }
    .searchRow input{
      height: 46px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.12);
      padding: 0 14px;
      font-size: 15px;
      outline: none;
      background: white;
    }
    .searchRow input:focus{ border-color: rgba(24, 90, 220, .35); box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(24, 90, 220, .12); }
    .searchRow button{
      height: 46px;
      padding: 0 18px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #2b66ff, #1748d8);
      color: white;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(23, 72, 216, .22);
    }
    .heroMeta{
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
      color: rgba(0,0,0,.62);
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .dot{ opacity: .55; }

    .taxScope{ padding: 34px 0 72px; }
    .grid{
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }
    .featureCard{
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-rows: 160px auto;
    }
    .media{
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,.18), rgba(0,0,0,.10)),
        url("/assets/tax-card-individual.jpg");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: top center;
    }
    .media.alt{
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,.18), rgba(0,0,0,.10)),
        url("/assets/tax-card-business.jpg");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: top center;
    }
    .body{ padding: 18px 18px 20px; }
    .body h2{ margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    .muted{ margin: 0 0 12px; color: rgba(0,0,0,.62); }

    .checkList{ list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: grid; gap: 10px; }
    .checkList li{
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 34px;
      line-height: 1.3;
      color: rgba(0,0,0,.82);
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .checkList li::before{
      content: "✓";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: rgba(24, 160, 88, .10);
      color: #108a4b;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .ctaStrip{

      margin-top: 20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.92);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.05);
      padding: 18px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .ctaStrip h3{ margin: 0 0 4px; font-size: 18px; }
    .ctaStrip p{ margin: 0; }
    .ctaBtn{
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 42px;
      padding: 0 16px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: #0b1b35;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }


.taxExplain{ margin-top: 18px; }

    @media (max-width: 900px){
      h1{ font-size: 34px; }
      .grid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .ctaStrip{ flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
      .ctaBtn{ width: 100%; }
    }
  
    .infoBlock{ display: block; }
    .bulletList{
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: rgba(0,0,0,.72);
    }
    .bulletList li{ margin: 6px 0; }
    .qa{ margin-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08); padding-top: 12px; }
    .qa:first-of-type{ border-top: 0; padding-top: 0; }
    .qa .q{
      font-weight: 650;
      cursor: pointer;
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      user-select: none;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .qa .q::-webkit-details-marker{ display: none; }
    .qa .q::after{
      content: "▾";
      font-size: 14px;
      opacity: .65;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      transition: transform .18s ease;
    }
    details[open].qa .q::after{ transform: rotate(180deg) translateY(1px); }
    .qa .a{ margin-top: 10px; }

</style>

<style>
.infoBlock.centered h3 { text-align: center; }
.infoBlock.withImage { display: flex; gap: 32px; align-items: center; }
.infoBlock.withImage.left { flex-direction: row; }
.infoBlock.withImage.right { flex-direction: row-reverse; }
.infoBlock .image img { max-width: 220px; height: auto; opacity: 0.9; }
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .infoBlock.withImage { flex-direction: column; }
}
</style>

</SiteLayout>
